abstract: Police officer uses van to ram demonstrators protesting against United States outside US Embassy in Manila, injuring dozens of protesters.
lead_paragraph: Riot police officers roughed up people in a rally of about 1,000 activists in Manila who demanded an end to the United States presence in the Philippines.

headline.main: Philippine Police Van Rams Protesters at U.S. Embassy, Hurting Dozens
